  "prompt": "When did you know it was time to quit?",
  "response": "Knowing when it's time to quit can vary greatly for each person and situation. Common signs include feeling unfulfilled or unhappy, experiencing chronic stress or burnout, realizing that your values no longer align with your current circumstances, or seeing no opportunities for growth or advancement. Additionally, if you have a clear alternative path that excites you, that can also signal that it might be time to make a change. Ultimately, it's about assessing your personal feelings, goals, and circumstances to make the best decision for yourself.",
